Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.67,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}名も無き罪に　付けられた傷で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:17.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}心閉ざし　無理をして笑う
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:23.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}幸せな日々　君はどこかに捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:29.48,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}詩人のように　孤独　愛してた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533\fs22.667\pos(769.587,9.973)}い  ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533\pos(960,39.667)}色彩を奪われた　灰色の街
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:42.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}僕がいるよ　解き放って翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.54,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}抱きしめるから恐れないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.63,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}壊れるまで叫ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.55,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}神を殺す言葉さえここにはあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}2人交わり　ひとつになって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.93,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}裸足のまま歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:13.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}壁を越えた空の果て　聴こえてくる愛の歌が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:55.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}响彻乐园的歌声  回荡在我心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:10.67,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}无名之罪的枷锁  让人痛苦窒息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:17.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}强颜欢笑的背后  是内心筑起的孤寂高墙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:23.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}幸福的时光  已被你尘封于心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.47,0:01:29.48,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}如同诗人一般  爱上踽踽独行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:34.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}被剥夺了一切色彩的灰色街道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.70,0:01:42.08,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}有我在这  你不再是折翼的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.54,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}不用害怕  我会将你拥入怀中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:48.63,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}撕心裂肺般地呐喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:54.55,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}即便那是弑神之语  也有我与你一起肩负
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:57.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}化为一体的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.93,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}就这样赤足前进
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.14,0:02:13.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}一起谱写  这跨越一切障碍  震彻云霄的爱之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:11.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}羽が舞い散る静寂の場所
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:16.56,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}逃げるように消えてく影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:22.11,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}サヨナラが運命なのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:28.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}喜んで受け入れましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:38.79,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}読み捨てられた絵本のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:43.92,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}優しさ達滲んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:49.47,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}眠りにつくまで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.89,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}不器用な愛をあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:00.65,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}涙流すこと　笑うことさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:05.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}ぎこちない日から　おかしいでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:08.70,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}だれかと似ていて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}うまく生きれない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}また会えるのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:19.66,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}その時はすべて伝えたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}キミに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.38,0:22:11.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}在漫天飞羽的寂静之地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:16.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}如同逃走般消失的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:22.11,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}分别如果是命中注定的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:28.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}就请高兴地接受它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.99,0:22:38.79,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}仿佛匆匆过目的图画书一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.04,0:22:43.92,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}渗透着浓浓的温情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.21,0:22:49.47,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}直到你入睡为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:54.89,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}将我笨拙的爱传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.97,0:23:00.65,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}无论是伤心还是欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:05.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}从遭遇悲痛的那天起  我就变得不再是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:08.70,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}就像某人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}无法好好地生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.58,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}若是还能再相见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:19.66,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}想把心中的一切都
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:23.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,500)\blur4.533}告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:18:00.68,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}迷子の子供みたい  うつむいて泣いてたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:11.40,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}安心できる場所が  ようやく見つかった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:23.37,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}キミが残してくれた  記憶に抱かれて眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:37.09,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}みんなに伝えて欲しい  あの人を愛してる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:42.64,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}名前呼んでも　指で触れても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:48.56,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}からかうように　口付けしても
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:54.11,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}照れくさそうな  笑顔はもう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:19:06.45,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}なくて　どこを見てもいない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:18.22,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}少しだけ先歩くキミの後ろ追いかけて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:23.93,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}次に捕まえた時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:32.65,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}もう離さない　二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:18:00.68,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}如同迷路的孩子一般  眼泪划过垂下的两颊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:11.40,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}好不容易找到了  能使自己安心的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:23.37,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}如今却只能沉浸在  对你的回忆中入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:37.09,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}想要让大家知道  我深爱着那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.34,0:18:42.64,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}即便呼唤你的名字  即使用手指轻触
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:48.56,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}亦或是调皮般地轻轻一吻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.77,0:18:54.11,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}你那害羞般的笑容也已经
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:19:06.45,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}不复存在  消失在了彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:18.22,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}追寻着你先行一步的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:23.93,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}下次抓住你时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:32.65,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.533}再也不会将手松开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}坠崖第十三天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森同学误吃了花苗倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里已经第几天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第十三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖地睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊吹同学由于缺乏维生素  意识恍惚的时间增多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井同学出现了败血症的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,广冈同学已经连反应都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.96,0:00:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就这样沉睡下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心脏不再跳动的话该有多轻松啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在放弃还言之尚早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.06,0:00:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还不是地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界还有活下去的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:17.99,TXTE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(1091.075,106.667)}『坠崖第十四天』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经饿到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,之前吃的那点肉  反而激起了更强的食欲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样才能得救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我弟弟的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,风见…雄二？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这是我弟弟的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能活着回去  就介绍你认识
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定会喜欢他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是期待呢  说定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  失败了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,广冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,广冈同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:09.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这一天傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,广冈同学离开了人世
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去挖个坟把她埋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大家都变得奇怪起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:30.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中抱着她死了也是无可奈何的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个多么卑鄙的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:44.03,TXTE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(1091.476,118)}『坠崖第十五天』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人活着就会有死去的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这便是这个世界的绝对法则
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天樱井学姐和古森同学死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樱井学姐的死因是败血症
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,古森同学是自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,内心已经没有了悲痛  可怜之类的想法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只觉得又能少一个人吃饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:09.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金田学姐吃了伤口上的蛆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经完全变得不正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40.8}真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了逃避恐惧和饥饿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.61,0:04:18.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们产生了难以置信的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有谁能代替自己死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们就能得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  你赶快去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是  别客气赶快去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老师抓到了鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃掉这个  振作起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.76,0:04:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬  有鹿肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部长和老师抓到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,随便乱吃肉会得肝炎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经煮过了  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也不想活下来之后饱受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想做出背叛一姬的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此下决心放弃了吃那些肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  那天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:30.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部长和老师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是机会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,逃出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.69,0:05:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,离开这座山  回到家里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援已经不会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只能靠自己逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要挑现在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:52.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有时间给你细说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尽量快点收拾好行装
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别让其他人察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能带魔鬼一起走  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魔鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬  你带我去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,安静点跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让你看看真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别发出大的声响
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人  是这样的关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再仔细看看周围
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:06:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:06:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让她们逃了  杀了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,束缚他们的人类本性已经没了  互相残杀要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:42.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…一定是在做梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是别把他们当成人类比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时间你们要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.36,0:07:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐久间学姐  部长和老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  这个人已经没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.29,0:08:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  你们看到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佐久间学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经和你说过了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能带魔鬼一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人已经回不到人类的世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会  这一定不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾  周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经还挺喜欢你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:24.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的人已经不是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而是动物
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:32.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像狮子吃斑马是理所当然的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斑马不会因此生气或者哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,弱肉强食  这便是世界的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是答应过你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会把你救出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.97,0:08:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别躲躲藏藏的  快出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,金田学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs40.8}都是误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.02,0:09:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是变为魔鬼了  还是被魔鬼所骗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管如何  那个人也已经回不来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好好和我说  我会理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.78,0:09:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,够了  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经害怕得动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,与其被抓住杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:44.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个使命就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说我去做诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面有我偷藏的食物和盐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我把能活着逃出深山的办法写在了上面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要好好的看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:09.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别放弃  往前走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.29,0:10:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧  为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要  要抛弃我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.64,0:10:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会再见的  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬一个人逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经很累了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:28.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要听我的话  一定会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.40,0:10:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要回头  赶紧离开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:57.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一心想要让自己获救  而舍弃了一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬会被杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是活着遭受最痛苦的方式而死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了救我这样胆小的女人而牺牲了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最后看见的一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有哭喊  也没有用怨恨的眼神看着我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.15,0:11:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在微笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛在笑着说  这就是命运  这就是法则
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.13,TXTE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)\pos(1081.742,144)}『坠崖第XX天』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后过了多少天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬的背包里有她偷偷藏起来的点心零食
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没有动那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一姬有幸能逃出生天追上我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把这些全都还给她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是现在就屈服吃了这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟那些饿鬼们没有区别了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有「不能白费这条被一姬救下的命」这个念头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,支撑着我在森林里彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我  一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:41.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家肯定是来带我到天国去的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  我走不动了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧  我真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  我牺牲了许许多多的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,独自一人不知廉耻地活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从事故生还的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被媒体当成奇迹的生还来报道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.93,0:13:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但立刻有人开始怀疑我生还的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有你活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:58.90,TXTF,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz277.6\pos(1566.44,398.8)}剖析得以生还的\N少女A的阴暗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:13:59.69,TXTF,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz289.6\pos(1168.013,4.933)}验证！\N从现场的碎尸中分析
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:00.44,TXTF,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz244.4\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\pos(1271.084,92)}在食物耗尽后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.40,0:14:05.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亏你还能装作没事一样生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.03,0:14:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,换成我肯定不会干这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.24,0:14:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要那么做还不如死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好想活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:25.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有你得救
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你不救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.34,0:14:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是对活下来的我的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲他人而活下来的我必须接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:43.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不比死掉的人更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会有人认同我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一个人来惩罚活下来的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要一个人成为我活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那时  最适合给我惩罚的男人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.75,0:15:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫风见雄二  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起一直瞒着你  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是牺牲了你的姐姐而活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知廉耻的卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我第一次见到你的时候就想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我从雄二身边夺走了一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那至少让我代替她陪在你身边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二想要我做的事我什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说  你接近我的动机是对我有愧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而并非恋爱感情对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.50,0:15:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老实说  虽然我不讨厌雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还没发展到喜欢的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此  我只要能跟雄二在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能给雄二付出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得自己的罪好像减轻了一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能不相信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可我真的  喜欢上了雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我喜欢上雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被你索求就算不上惩罚了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我会感到幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想应该到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:26.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算把一切都告诉雄二然后离开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:30.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管我怎么道歉一姬都回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.42,0:16:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:33.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  你能不能杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有这样才能受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有这样才能得到宽恕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能让雄二杀了我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.49,0:16:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  就这样也喊痛的女人还敢叫我杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.67,0:17:08.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你这话  不要再说对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  我的姐姐只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着你代替一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是让你不要再说了吗白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你等等  让我思考一会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:35.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到头来  你就是喜欢我对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  天音  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先我要说的是  我没打算同情你的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.84,0:17:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是谁只要活着或多或少都会有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.84,0:17:58.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也明白你的过去不是「后悔」就能形容的小事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对这样一辈子都活在痛苦里后悔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么忘掉它或别在意之类的废话肯定一点用都没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说让我杀了你对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你的命我就收下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:17.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你今后一辈子都要为了我而活
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是对你的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为我奉献一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是你的国王  你的饲主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你听懂了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永远跟我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以呆在雄二身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你敢擅自离开我才不饶你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊  哭时的脸真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好过分  这种时候你就让人家哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧好吧  不过太吵了我只能批准你哭5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二太不温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.61,0:19:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太温柔那还能算惩罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.53,0:19:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能拯救天音的方法只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.20,0:19:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是接受她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知悉她的过去  接受她的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那样她总有一天会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能宽恕自己的  只有自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到她明白的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就呆在她身边  成为她的惩罚好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是全世界都不原谅天音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让我一个人原谅她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.81,0:19:32.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话  天音能原谅她自己的那天就肯定会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐  天音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你真觉得一姬死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:45.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬的尸体被切碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可找不到头部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.96,0:19:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是一个参考数据
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.38,0:19:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,假如有十个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.67,0:19:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就能伪装成十一个人的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:19:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那一姬她还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我无论如何都想像不到那个一姬会乖乖受死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一姬给我的密林逃脱法小抄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她让我如果逃不出去就回到居留点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上面写有藏着应急食品的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.70,0:20:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来一姬从一开始藏着几分让天音逃脱的打算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是一姬还活着的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:31.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得证据一定会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确实没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  我们去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,回到那现场吗  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.42,0:20:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我总有一天要克服的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  我觉得只要跟雄二一起就不会有事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去买供奉用的花和香火
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先在这等等我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您是风见雄二先生对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  您是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫坂下  是天音的粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟她是相当出名的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:15.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说她最近交到了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我冒昧  请问您的工作是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到不久前我还是个IT相关企业的董事长来着
